{"tid":344020,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[被失蹤] 曾闖西沙島12海浬 美導彈驅逐艦水兵南海失蹤","createTime":"2017-08-02T03:03:59.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-02T04:46:39.000Z","uid":77196,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"61d083320126d8aa9c1d37fc21b2be63690b95ee","tid":344020,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T03:03:59.000Z","msg":"美國廣播公司報道稱，美國導彈驅逐艦「斯特西姆號」（USS Stethem），<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>昨晨在南海執行例行任務期間，有一名海軍士兵失蹤</strong></span>。美國和日本船艦和飛機正在搜尋這名失蹤士兵，但美國官方沒有公佈這名水兵的姓名。<br />\n<br />\n報道稱，「斯特西姆號」號在昨晨9時許接獲該名水兵的失蹤報告，隨即在艦上進行多次搜索，試圖找到該名失蹤水兵，但未有發現。該艦的母港為日本橫須賀港，日本海上自衞隊亦派遣直升機母艦「出雲號」及高波級導彈驅逐艦「漣號」加入搜索。美國海軍說，夏威夷人員救援聯合中心也在協助搜尋工作。<br />\n<br />\n據悉，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>美國官員在上月2日指，斯特西姆號曾駛入中國南海西沙群島的中建島12海浬範圍內</strong></span>。中國外交部事後予以譴責，並強烈敦促美方立即停止此類嚴重侵犯中國主權、威脅中國安全的挑釁行動。"},{"pid":"5fd72d503c472230c9cf29dbe5d806c526a25509","tid":344020,"uid":95577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T03:06:07.000Z","msg":"盧溝橋事件<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n快啲要求去南沙起緊嘅工地搵人啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e1f9e894ee332f8b8377d4d3f63ea562dbd224d","tid":344020,"uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T03:07:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>盧溝橋事件<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n快啲要求去南沙起緊嘅工地搵人啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n偽旗行動"},{"pid":"62f5ef6e80a0c85e0723ba8e6709cdc638e73b17","tid":344020,"uid":119494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T03:33:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd0459fc6650fa43c8f7e5638a30d3b6f8444726","tid":344020,"uid":25424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T03:37:35.000Z","msg":"美國快D出曬直昇機全方位搜索啦"},{"pid":"c3860b2fead6a73f4d0ff87d94783bceaa166a90","tid":344020,"uid":113929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T04:03:53.000Z","msg":"918事變<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a78ce37e45431ef2474fe6f250a0ccd8763e640","tid":344020,"uid":119494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T04:46:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>美國快D出曬直昇機全方位搜索啦</blockquote><br />\n派兵上海南島 廣東沿岸 一帶搜索<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}